text: Ate alaha ne tuhade la'i tuhade gharam nu amana da sathana bana'i'a ate tuhade la'i janavaram di khala de ghara (kheme? Bana'e. Jinham nu tusim apane saphara daurana ate para'a daurana saukhe dhaga nala varatade ho ate unham di una, unham di ru ate unham de valam tom ghara da samana ate labhada'ika vasatu'am ika samem la'i bana'i'am)
